Physical security could be in the form of defending a building with fences, bollards, surveillance systems, access control entries, door locks, and other defences. 

## In this section of the course,

we're going to be focused on physical security

including its security control measures,

the attacks focused

against the physical security of our networks,

and methods to counter these types of attacks.

Now, physical security refers to measures taken to

protect tangible assets like your buildings, your equipment,

your people from any kind of harm or unauthorized access.

